WEBVTT

00:11.667 --> 00:14.291
(gunshot)
FRANK: Van is dead.

00:14.375 --> 00:16.000
Fucking murdered an FBI agent.

00:16.083 --> 00:16.709
I want you to kill my father.

00:16.792 --> 00:18.000
Why me, Raymond?

00:18.083 --> 00:20.417
'Cause I want
the last person he sees

00:20.500 --> 00:21.750
to hate him as much as I do.

00:21.834 --> 00:24.333
It's all there.

00:24.417 --> 00:25.500
Where'd you get it?

00:25.583 --> 00:27.125
Ruth's foundation.

00:27.208 --> 00:27.583
Sully just called.

00:27.667 --> 00:29.750
It's been done.

00:29.834 --> 00:31.208
RAY:
I'll get your money.

00:31.291 --> 00:34.333
You got the wrong guy, pal.
What are you
talking about?

00:34.417 --> 00:35.041
And I can prove it.

00:35.125 --> 00:37.917
Seany boy, are you in there?

00:38.000 --> 00:39.083
Let me in.

00:39.166 --> 00:42.250
Mickey, please, help me.

00:42.333 --> 00:42.625
I can't, kid.

00:42.709 --> 00:43.792
(gunshot)

00:43.875 --> 00:45.834
What happened, Raymond?

00:45.917 --> 00:46.959
Sully.

00:47.041 --> 00:48.458
And Mickey's still alive.

00:48.542 --> 00:49.542
Ruth's money?

00:49.625 --> 00:50.208
Gone.

00:50.291 --> 00:52.417
We've unleashed a monster.

00:52.500 --> 00:53.333
He doesn't have a
passport. I'll find him.

00:55.375 --> 00:57.083
Do you think
Sully's coming for us?

00:57.166 --> 00:59.041
I'm going into town.
You take care of the kids.

00:59.125 --> 01:02.166
I can't let
you do that.
Are we in danger?

01:02.250 --> 01:03.375
BUNCHY:
Remember me?

01:03.458 --> 01:04.625
It's Brendan.

01:04.709 --> 01:05.917
We don't know each other.

01:06.000 --> 01:07.667
I'm sorry.
Are you?

01:07.750 --> 01:09.208
RAY:
What'd you do?

01:09.291 --> 01:10.750
It was an accident.

01:10.834 --> 01:12.000
What the fuck?

01:12.083 --> 01:13.291
I need help.

01:13.375 --> 01:14.458
Bunchy shot him.

01:14.542 --> 01:16.458
He won't take me
to the hospital.

01:16.542 --> 01:17.208
They don't know, do they?

01:17.291 --> 01:19.959
Shut up.
You never told them.

01:20.041 --> 01:21.417
I told you to shut up.

01:21.500 --> 01:22.500
I loved you.

01:23.500 --> 01:26.834
FRANCES:
So you took him
to the hospital?

01:26.917 --> 01:28.166
Yeah.

01:28.250 --> 01:29.542
Which hospital?

01:31.875 --> 01:33.792
I had Avi take the kids
to a hotel.

01:33.875 --> 01:35.166
Okay.
Ray, that priest--
what happened?

01:35.250 --> 01:37.625
Is that the one
that abused Bunchy?

01:37.709 --> 01:39.375
Wasn't only Bunch.

01:42.583 --> 01:43.959
No. No, no.

01:44.041 --> 01:46.041
Don't touch me.

01:54.542 --> 01:58.834
♪ ♪

01:58.917 --> 02:00.959
(tires screech)

02:04.083 --> 02:05.583
There he is.

02:10.291 --> 02:12.667
(horn honking)
♪ Rock steady, baby ♪

02:12.750 --> 02:15.542
♪ That's what I feel now ♪

02:15.625 --> 02:17.250
♪ Let's call this song
exactly what it is ♪

