♪ Rock steady ♪

03:17.667 --> 03:20.291
Eddie!

03:20.375 --> 03:23.417
♪ Let's call this song
exactly what it is ♪

03:23.500 --> 03:25.709
♪ What it is, what it is,
what it is...  ♪

03:25.792 --> 03:27.709
(grunts)

03:27.792 --> 03:30.250
(people murmuring)

03:36.625 --> 03:37.750
Call an ambulance.

03:37.834 --> 03:40.375
Back away.

03:40.458 --> 03:41.125
Get back!

03:41.208 --> 03:43.625
Please. Please, everybody back.

03:43.709 --> 03:45.917
Okay, if you would, please,
everybody back.

03:46.000 --> 03:47.458
Where's Sully?

03:47.542 --> 03:49.125
I... I don't know.

03:49.208 --> 03:50.917
(groaning)

03:51.000 --> 03:52.125
It's all right.
He know CPR.

03:52.208 --> 03:53.250
Where's Sully, Eddie?

03:53.333 --> 03:54.375
AVI:
He knows what he's doing.

03:54.458 --> 03:55.542
Santa Monica.
Where?

03:55.625 --> 03:55.917
I don't know.

03:56.000 --> 03:57.834
(groans)

03:57.917 --> 03:59.375
My God, I'm dying here.

03:59.458 --> 04:01.583
Tell me how to find him,
and I'll stop.

04:01.667 --> 04:02.583
Uh, all you can eat.

04:02.667 --> 04:04.625
(groans)

04:04.709 --> 04:05.208
What?

04:05.291 --> 04:06.750
AVI:
Everything's okay.

04:06.834 --> 04:08.500
Tiny.

04:08.583 --> 04:08.959
All you can eat.

04:09.041 --> 04:11.250
Third Street.

04:11.333 --> 04:13.709
MAN: Yeah, I see him.
AVI: Everybody back, thank you.

04:13.792 --> 04:16.208
Okay, folks, stand back.

04:16.291 --> 04:19.208
Be smart, keep your mouth shut,
and we'll take care of you.

04:19.291 --> 04:21.917
(panting)

04:27.083 --> 04:28.542
Don't say anything, Raymond.

04:33.583 --> 04:36.709
(sighs) I waited all night for
you to come arrest me, Frank.

04:36.792 --> 04:37.834
What are you doing here?

04:37.917 --> 04:40.667
I thought you might need
your lawyer, motherfucker.

04:40.750 --> 04:42.125
Van was a good agent.

04:42.208 --> 04:44.458
A good American.
All right.

04:45.792 --> 04:46.667
(sighs)

04:46.750 --> 04:49.959
Let's go.

04:52.041 --> 04:54.542
You're not gonna
bring me in, Frank.

04:54.625 --> 04:56.834
'Cause you know
I didn't do it.

04:56.917 --> 04:59.208
You think I'd leave a body?

04:59.291 --> 05:01.125
You think I'm that stupid?

05:01.208 --> 05:02.750
I don't leave fucking evidence.

05:02.834 --> 05:04.083
That's not admissible.

05:04.166 --> 05:05.709
You haven't
Mirandized him.

05:05.792 --> 05:07.083
You pursue this, you're gonna
look like an asshole,

05:07.166 --> 05:09.542
and you're gonna
lose your pension.

05:09.625 --> 05:11.750
You want to be an asshole
with no pension,

05:11.834 --> 05:13.208
that's fine with me, Frank,

05:13.291 --> 05:15.083
but who's gonna support
those kids of yours?

05:15.166 --> 05:16.959
Do not fucking
do this to me, Ray.

05:17.041 --> 05:18.875
I think you're gonna
give me 12 hours,

05:18.959 --> 05:21.041
'cause you know
I'm telling the truth.

05:29.250 --> 05:30.625
(sighs)

05:34.792 --> 05:37.083
You're making
the right decision, Frank.

05:37.166 --> 05:38.667
12 hours.

06:07.792 --> 06:10.166
You all right?

06:12.333 --> 06:14.458
Thought I'd feel real bad after
what happened to Father Danny.

06:17.834 --> 06:18.709
But I don't.

06:21.709 --> 06:23.959
I'm glad he's gone.

06:24.041 --> 06:26.667
That way, he can't
do it to anyone else.

06:28.125 --> 06:32.458
That's right, Bunch.

06:33.542 --> 06:36.667
I'm gonna stay
at my apartment from now on.

06:37.875 --> 06:39.083
Good.

06:39.166 --> 06:40.834
Won't be mad?

06:40.917 --> 06:43.000
No. Course not.

06:43.083 --> 06:44.542
But you change your mind,

06:44.625 --> 06:47.083
you're welcome here any time,
you know that.

06:47.166 --> 06:49.500
Thanks, Ter.

06:57.333 --> 06:59.709
(waves sloshing)

07:05.333 --> 07:08.000
You are taking
advantage.

07:08.083 --> 07:09.834
Who do you think is gonna
pay for all of this?

07:09.917 --> 07:12.458
Dad?

07:12.542 --> 07:14.834
Dad's not here, Conor.

07:14.917 --> 07:17.583
You're gonna make
yourself sick.

07:17.667 --> 07:19.709
Plus, you're not even
hungry, you're sad.

07:19.792 --> 07:21.792
Bullshit. Sad about what?

07:21.875 --> 07:23.125
Mom and Dad.

07:23.208 --> 07:24.709
Why?

07:24.792 --> 07:28.166
Mom's upset, Dad's gone.

07:28.250 --> 07:31.208
Uh, we're staying in a hotel,
we're missing school.

07:31.291 --> 07:33.417
So what?
I don't even like school.

07:33.500 --> 07:36.583
If I was in Israel,
I'd be in the army right now.

07:36.667 --> 07:37.792
You are clueless.

07:37.875 --> 07:40.375
(scoffs)

07:44.917 --> 07:46.250
Mommy?

07:46.333 --> 07:49.000
Come on, it's
time to get up.

07:49.959 --> 07:53.291
Mom?

07:53.375 --> 07:55.834
Leave me alone, Bridget.

07:55.917 --> 07:57.083
Where's Dad?

07:57.166 --> 07:58.875
I don't know.

07:58.959 --> 08:02.375
When are we going home?

08:02.458 --> 08:02.959
Mom, you should get up.

08:03.041 --> 08:05.792
Leave me alone!

08:06.125 --> 08:07.834
(sighs)

08:07.917 --> 08:10.750
(sniffles)

08:13.792 --> 08:14.625
LENA:
You write that one down?
3832 Wilshire Blvd?

08:14.709 --> 08:16.959
Did you find
the "all you can eat" yet?

08:17.041 --> 08:18.041
We're working on it.

08:18.125 --> 08:20.750
How hard can it be?
Boss, there's a bunch of 'em.

08:20.834 --> 08:21.959
So narrow it down.

08:22.041 --> 08:23.000
Show his fucking picture.

08:23.083 --> 08:25.083
The guy weighs 300 pounds,
for Christ's sake.

08:25.166 --> 08:27.166
Everybody who eats in these
places weighs 300 pounds.

08:27.250 --> 08:30.291
We're running out of time,
all right?

08:30.375 --> 08:33.291
Okay. All right, look,
we're going now.

08:33.375 --> 08:35.083
We just had
to collect all the names.

08:35.166 --> 08:36.625
Maybe he meant
Third Street in Hollywood.

08:36.709 --> 08:37.250
No, they stayed in Santa Monica.

08:37.333 --> 08:39.417
He hides in plain sight.

08:39.500 --> 08:41.291
That's how he did it in Boston.

08:41.375 --> 08:42.917
He doesn't run,
he doesn't go far.

08:43.000 --> 08:44.583
He's right there.
Just fucking find him.

08:44.667 --> 08:46.125
Okay.
We will, Ray.

08:46.208 --> 08:47.500
I'll meet you
downstairs.
Yeah.

08:47.583 --> 08:49.583
You want me to
check on your family?

08:49.667 --> 08:51.750
No, they're all right.

08:51.834 --> 08:54.125
Did you call Abby?

08:54.208 --> 08:55.917
What are you,
my fucking marriage counselor?

08:56.000 --> 08:58.417
Go out there
and do your fucking job!

08:59.333 --> 09:01.583
(door slams)

09:07.834 --> 09:10.583
What the fuck are you doing?

09:11.417 --> 09:13.291
This is not
appropriate for me.

09:13.375 --> 09:16.000
I'm a sexual anorexic.

09:16.083 --> 09:18.291
Oh, come on.
Enough with that shit.

09:18.375 --> 09:21.417
Jesus.

09:21.500 --> 09:23.417
What the hell?

09:23.500 --> 09:25.792
You know what, Pop?

09:25.875 --> 09:28.875
I don't want you
here no more.

09:28.959 --> 09:30.709
I want my place back.

09:30.792 --> 09:34.166
Really?

09:41.709 --> 09:44.667
We have good times,
don't we, Bunch?

09:44.750 --> 09:46.875
I thought we were having
fun being together.

09:50.750 --> 09:51.834
All right, you know what?

09:51.917 --> 09:55.667
You take the bed,
have your privacy, you're right.

09:55.750 --> 09:57.959
I can move back out
to the couch.

09:58.041 --> 09:59.500
No.

09:59.583 --> 10:02.000
I want to live alone.

10:02.083 --> 10:03.333
Like a grown-up.

10:03.417 --> 10:04.875
I see.

10:04.959 --> 10:07.583
Well, just be careful
you don't burn it down.

10:07.667 --> 10:10.333
See? That's what
I'm talking about.

10:10.417 --> 10:12.709
Why you got to bring that up?

10:12.792 --> 10:14.875
It's just a bolt out of
the fucking blue, that's all.

10:14.959 --> 10:16.792
I told you
Father Danny was here.

10:16.875 --> 10:18.583
You should have
listened to me.

10:18.667 --> 10:22.083
This... this wouldn't
have happened.

10:22.166 --> 10:24.709
What wouldn't have happened?

10:26.417 --> 10:30.583
I got fucking drunk...

10:30.667 --> 10:32.291
and I shot him.

10:32.375 --> 10:34.333
You what?

10:34.417 --> 10:36.542
Ray had to take
care of it.

10:36.625 --> 10:40.083
He killed him
right in front of us.

10:40.166 --> 10:42.667
It really fucked up Terry.

10:42.750 --> 10:45.709
And it really fucked up me.

10:48.166 --> 10:49.125
How's Ray feel about it?

10:49.208 --> 10:51.458
I don't know.

10:51.542 --> 10:53.917
Why don't you fucking ask him?

10:54.000 --> 10:55.500
All right, I will.

10:56.583 --> 10:58.750
Jesus, ain't
that something.

11:00.000 --> 11:01.875
It was really him, huh?

11:09.000 --> 11:12.166
Maybe you're right.

11:12.250 --> 11:15.083
Maybe I am a bad influence.

11:15.166 --> 11:18.250
It's just a lot
of bad shit's been happening

11:18.333 --> 11:19.917
since you got here.

11:45.375 --> 11:47.500
How old are you?

11:49.250 --> 11:50.959
I'm 65.

11:51.041 --> 11:53.000
You got any I.D. on you?

11:53.083 --> 11:54.625
Like a... driver's license?

11:54.709 --> 11:56.125
Social Security card?

11:56.625 --> 11:58.208
Sure, I got I.D.

11:58.291 --> 12:00.458
You got cash?

12:03.125 --> 12:04.291
300 bucks?

12:04.375 --> 12:07.000
Let's go.

12:07.083 --> 12:08.959
(door creaks)

12:25.709 --> 12:26.834
(chuckles)

12:26.917 --> 12:27.417
You fucking kidding me?

12:27.500 --> 12:30.000
I want your wallet.

12:30.083 --> 12:31.000
And I want your sneakers.

12:45.583 --> 12:48.375
(grunting)

12:48.458 --> 12:50.291
WOMAN:
...roast the perfect turkey,

12:50.375 --> 12:51.875
preheat the oven to 325...

12:51.959 --> 12:53.667
Where's Eddie?

12:53.750 --> 12:56.625
I need him to go to the mall
and buy me new sneakers.

12:56.709 --> 12:58.208
You know how hard
these were to find?

12:58.291 --> 12:58.875
(keys clatter)

12:58.959 --> 13:00.000
(sighs)
My fucking feet.

13:02.792 --> 13:04.792
My arches just
keep collapsing.

13:05.750 --> 13:07.166
(sighs)

13:07.250 --> 13:09.417
Where is he?

13:10.375 --> 13:12.083
He left.

13:15.750 --> 13:16.417
He take the money?

13:16.500 --> 13:18.291
He only took one bag.

13:18.375 --> 13:20.250
He took one bag?!

13:20.333 --> 13:21.834
You fat fuck!
(shouts)

13:21.917 --> 13:24.333
You fat motherfucker!
(grunting)

13:24.417 --> 13:25.875
What the...
Huh?

13:25.959 --> 13:27.417
You're fucking dead!

13:27.500 --> 13:29.500
You fucking piece of shit!

13:29.583 --> 13:30.125
(sobbing)

13:33.583 --> 13:36.875
I just slit a guy's throat,
and all I got was a fucking...

13:36.959 --> 13:39.458
Ralphs card.

13:42.125 --> 13:44.709
Fuck am I gonna do?

13:46.750 --> 13:48.917
Well...

13:49.000 --> 13:50.709
now you're gonna have
to go to the mall

13:50.792 --> 13:53.208
and get me my new sneakers.

13:53.291 --> 13:56.834
All right.

13:56.917 --> 13:58.083
I got to eat, Sully;
I'm starving.

13:58.166 --> 14:01.083
Yeah. What, you're starving?
Jesus fucking...

14:01.166 --> 14:03.125
Okay, it's a size 12.
And, here, it...

14:06.166 --> 14:09.917
46 and a... half, U.K.

14:12.792 --> 14:15.959
Now, we get to the Maldives...

14:16.041 --> 14:19.291
this will be like a bad dream.

14:21.333 --> 14:22.291
You're still taking me?

14:22.375 --> 14:25.500
Yeah, fucking of course
I'm still taking you.

14:25.583 --> 14:27.166
You think I'm gonna...

14:27.250 --> 14:30.250
make friends
with the freakin' Maldivians?

14:30.333 --> 14:31.333
Learn a new fucking language?

14:31.417 --> 14:35.458
Forget it.

14:35.542 --> 14:37.458
I'm sorry I hit you
with the shoe.

14:37.542 --> 14:39.542
I got upset.
(scoffs)

14:39.625 --> 14:41.375
It was a cruel thing to do.

14:41.458 --> 14:42.417
Won't happen again.

14:42.500 --> 14:45.041
Okay, Sully.

14:45.125 --> 14:46.625
Okay.

14:46.709 --> 14:48.625
(exhales)

14:48.709 --> 14:51.083
(phone beeping)

14:55.333 --> 14:57.750
(ringtone playing)

15:04.375 --> 15:05.792
Hi, Grandpa.

15:05.875 --> 15:08.083
Conor, where's your dad?

15:08.166 --> 15:10.458
Uh, where he always is.
I don't know.

15:10.542 --> 15:12.500
How about your mom?

15:12.583 --> 15:14.083
Uh, we're at this big hotel.

15:14.166 --> 15:16.500
She's still in bed.
Something's wrong with her.

15:17.041 --> 15:20.125
What's the name of it?

15:35.083 --> 15:36.417
You all right?

15:36.917 --> 15:40.000
I lied to Frances.

15:41.834 --> 15:43.458
It's gonna tear us apart.

15:44.667 --> 15:47.250
Maybe not.
No.

15:47.333 --> 15:49.250
It will.

15:52.333 --> 15:54.834
We did what had to be done.

15:54.917 --> 15:56.792
Murder, Ray?

15:58.667 --> 16:00.500
I can't condone it.

16:05.083 --> 16:09.333
You should've told me
what happened to you.

16:09.417 --> 16:11.709
(chuckles)

16:13.625 --> 16:15.125
Yeah?

16:17.250 --> 16:20.792
You should've told somebody
when it happened to you.

16:20.875 --> 16:23.291
Might have
stopped him, Ter.

16:24.959 --> 16:28.000
I didn't know
what to make of it.

16:28.083 --> 16:31.500
I broke his fingers
and that was that.

16:34.125 --> 16:36.792
I didn't have words for it.

16:39.792 --> 16:41.125
I'm sorry.

16:49.166 --> 16:51.208
What do you want to do?

16:53.375 --> 16:54.875
About what?

16:54.959 --> 16:57.250
(sighs)

16:57.333 --> 16:59.291
The nurse.

17:02.291 --> 17:05.625
I think you got
to let her go, Ter.

17:06.333 --> 17:09.500
That's easy for you to say.

17:09.583 --> 17:12.375
You got a family.

17:12.458 --> 17:13.667
(door opens)

17:13.750 --> 17:15.625
(phone vibrating)

17:19.083 --> 17:19.542
Yeah.

17:19.625 --> 17:22.041
We found it.

17:22.125 --> 17:23.083
He comes every day
as soon as the buffet opens,

17:23.166 --> 17:24.917
and he's always
the first in line.

17:25.000 --> 17:27.333
Tell Avi to meet me there.

