35:22.750 --> 35:24.208
You loved us so much,

35:24.291 --> 35:26.333
how come you didn't
give us the money, huh?

35:26.417 --> 35:27.875
She needed it more.

35:28.000 --> 35:30.208
I knew you'd make it,
take care of the others.

35:30.291 --> 35:31.875
Bunchy and Terry, no way.

35:31.959 --> 35:32.667
They're weak.

35:32.750 --> 35:36.375
But you?

35:36.458 --> 35:39.291
You're my favorite, Ray.

35:39.375 --> 35:41.333
(voice breaking):
You always were.

35:41.417 --> 35:43.875
We're alike,
the two of us.

35:43.959 --> 35:46.375
Same exactly.

35:51.959 --> 35:54.083
(scoffs softly)

36:06.750 --> 36:09.917
I told you.

36:13.834 --> 36:17.458
I told you what happened
with that man.

36:17.542 --> 36:19.375
O'Connor.

36:24.166 --> 36:27.375
Remember what you did, Mick?

36:31.208 --> 36:32.291
Huh?

36:35.417 --> 36:38.792
You called me a liar,
and you beat the shit out of me.

36:38.875 --> 36:42.250
Remember that?

36:42.333 --> 36:44.750
You didn't stop him.

36:44.834 --> 36:48.333
And he kept after me
and kept after me.

36:52.583 --> 36:54.500
And then he went after Bunchy.

36:58.834 --> 37:00.959
Our sweet Bunchy.

37:02.875 --> 37:04.375
That's when I decided
to kill you, Mick.

37:08.291 --> 37:10.709
You been dead to me
since that day.

37:12.458 --> 37:16.250
You been dead to me
since I was ten years old.

37:20.208 --> 37:23.166
I'm sorry from the bottom
of my heart, Ray.

37:25.458 --> 37:26.834
(scoffs)

37:26.917 --> 37:27.959
There's no forgiveness for you,
you prick.

37:28.041 --> 37:30.500
Get the fuck out of here.

37:30.583 --> 37:32.500
(door opens)

37:42.625 --> 37:44.917
It's on. They called.

37:45.000 --> 37:47.750
Want to meet
at the marina.

37:47.834 --> 37:50.083
What's your plan, boy?

38:18.291 --> 38:19.583
Hey!

38:25.125 --> 38:27.041
That's a nice bike.

38:27.125 --> 38:29.208
Raleigh chopper.

38:29.291 --> 38:30.583
Yeah. Ape hangers.

38:34.041 --> 38:36.583
I didn't steal it.

38:36.667 --> 38:38.166
Somebody left it.

38:38.250 --> 38:39.917
It's okay.

38:40.000 --> 38:42.333
I just wanted to look at it.

38:42.417 --> 38:43.959
I got to go home.

38:44.041 --> 38:46.792
I'm not stopping you.

38:58.000 --> 39:00.792
♪ ♪

39:28.166 --> 39:31.583
I couldn't sleep last night.

39:34.458 --> 39:37.291
I didn't do the right thing
leaving him with you.

39:42.208 --> 39:44.625
What happened to him?

39:47.125 --> 39:50.208
The priest died.

39:50.291 --> 39:51.667
After you took him
to the hospital?

39:54.500 --> 39:56.709
We didn't get
to take him.

39:56.792 --> 39:58.208
Why not?

40:01.709 --> 40:02.875
It's complicated.

40:02.959 --> 40:06.291
Did you kill him?

40:06.375 --> 40:09.083
(sighs)

40:09.166 --> 40:10.792
Jesus, Terry.

40:10.875 --> 40:13.041
Are you gonna tell me
what happened, or aren't you?

40:13.125 --> 40:15.875
I... I can't.

40:17.041 --> 40:19.625
Something happened.

40:19.709 --> 40:20.250
I know something happened.

40:20.333 --> 40:23.917
Bunchy shot him. Why?

40:24.000 --> 40:24.583
He had his reasons.

40:27.417 --> 40:30.792
There's things that...

40:30.875 --> 40:31.667
that I can't talk about.

40:31.750 --> 40:33.959
If you can't
talk about these things,

40:34.041 --> 40:35.000
then how can anything ever...

40:35.083 --> 40:37.375
Jesus, woman!

40:37.458 --> 40:39.125
This is who I am!

40:39.208 --> 40:41.667
We're loyal to each other!

40:41.750 --> 40:45.667
If that's a problem,
then it's a problem!

40:47.792 --> 40:48.750
It's a problem.

40:54.000 --> 40:56.709
One more thing.

40:56.792 --> 40:59.041
What did you do with the body?

40:59.125 --> 41:01.166
We got rid of it.

41:05.291 --> 41:07.750
What do you expect me to do
with this information?

41:07.834 --> 41:10.208
I don't know, Frances.

41:12.834 --> 41:15.291
Do what you need to do.

41:21.208 --> 41:23.583
(crickets chirping)

41:31.792 --> 41:33.291
Think Sully's gonna show?

41:33.375 --> 41:34.709
I don't know.

41:34.792 --> 41:37.125
Did you call your wife?

41:37.208 --> 41:40.166
What the fuck's
the matter with you?

41:57.333 --> 41:59.583
What you looking
so surprised for, Ray?

41:59.667 --> 42:01.333
My life here is over.

42:01.417 --> 42:03.375
I convinced
my old pal here

42:03.458 --> 42:06.208
to take me with him.

42:09.959 --> 42:11.959
You're not setting me up,
are you, Ray?

42:15.875 --> 42:17.750
Ha-ah.

42:30.125 --> 42:31.166
Money first, Sully.

42:34.041 --> 42:36.375
Go.

42:39.959 --> 42:41.875
(Sully sighs)

42:41.959 --> 42:44.375
Hi, Avi.

42:44.458 --> 42:46.208
How's your mom?
She's fine, thanks...

42:46.291 --> 42:46.792
(groans)

42:52.500 --> 42:55.458
That's to show you not
to fuck with me, Ray.

42:55.542 --> 42:58.625
Where's the boat?

42:58.709 --> 42:59.625
Now let's go.

42:59.709 --> 43:00.667
You go first.

43:00.750 --> 43:02.792
Move it!

43:04.750 --> 43:05.542
Mick,

43:05.625 --> 43:08.834
lend a hand with
that, will you?

43:23.875 --> 43:25.709
♪ ♪

43:36.417 --> 43:38.291
What the fuck, Ray?

43:38.375 --> 43:40.417
You, get the fuck
off the boat.

43:40.500 --> 43:43.250
I'm fucking FBI.

43:43.333 --> 43:46.208
And I'm FBI's Most Wanted,
so go fuck yourself.

43:47.750 --> 43:50.291
You shoot me, he shoots him.

43:57.166 --> 44:00.875
Mick... go get his gun.

44:08.417 --> 44:11.083
Give me the gun.

44:11.166 --> 44:13.250
Give me the gun.

44:29.333 --> 44:31.333
And I'm taking
all the money, Ray.

44:33.000 --> 44:34.583
Now get off the fucking...

44:36.542 --> 44:38.417
(grunts)

44:39.709 --> 44:40.917
(grunts)

44:41.667 --> 44:45.542
What the fuck you do that for?!

44:45.625 --> 44:47.417
You were just in a shoot-out
with Sully Sullivan.

44:47.500 --> 44:48.417
What do you think I did it for?

44:48.500 --> 44:51.208
Give him the gun, Mick.

44:51.291 --> 44:54.417
Right... right.

44:54.500 --> 44:56.709
Call an ambulance.

44:56.792 --> 44:58.125
I'm not calling
a fucking ambulance.

44:58.208 --> 44:59.250
You take him.

44:59.333 --> 45:00.792
How the fuck do
I explain what he's doing here?

45:00.875 --> 45:03.250
You hired us
to help you find Sully!

45:03.333 --> 45:04.000
Now call a fucking ambulance!

45:13.709 --> 45:15.583
(groaning)

45:15.667 --> 45:18.625
You all right?
I am all right.

45:18.709 --> 45:20.959
(groaning)

45:21.041 --> 45:23.959
I have a punctured
lung and broken ribs.

45:24.041 --> 45:25.625
Jesus, what are you, a doctor?

45:25.709 --> 45:27.583
I was a medic
in the army.

45:27.667 --> 45:29.458
Let me see.
You were?

45:29.542 --> 45:30.834
(screams)

45:30.917 --> 45:32.375
What are you screaming for?

45:32.458 --> 45:33.834
It fucking hurts.

45:33.917 --> 45:35.583
It's all right.
You're gonna be okay.

45:35.667 --> 45:37.000
You call that ambulance yet?!

45:37.083 --> 45:38.583
They're on their way!

45:38.667 --> 45:40.333
What do you want me to do
with this piece of shit?

45:40.417 --> 45:41.542
Your problem.

45:43.458 --> 45:45.667
You were never here.

45:45.750 --> 45:47.208
You understand?

45:47.291 --> 45:49.166
Get the fuck out.

45:55.083 --> 45:57.166
(reporters clamoring,
cameras clicking)

45:57.250 --> 45:59.166
(indistinct radio chatter)

46:13.041 --> 46:15.875
Saved your
life, Ray-Ray.

46:15.959 --> 46:17.834
Guess we're even now.

46:17.917 --> 46:19.083
Is that how
you see it, Mick?

46:22.250 --> 46:24.291
Ray-Ray.

46:31.041 --> 46:33.333
That should be enough
to get you a plane ticket

46:33.417 --> 46:35.542
and a couple months rent
somewhere.

46:35.625 --> 46:39.208
Well, it's all water under
the bridge now, ain't it?

46:39.291 --> 46:41.667
Bye, Mick.

46:42.417 --> 46:44.625
(engine starts)

46:44.709 --> 46:47.542
You know what
your problem is, Ray?

46:47.625 --> 46:48.834
You cling to the past.

46:48.917 --> 46:51.417
You got to...
you got to move on.

46:54.583 --> 46:56.750
(monitor beeping steadily)

47:13.250 --> 47:16.041
Hey. Hi.

47:19.291 --> 47:22.125
♪ ♪

47:46.375 --> 47:48.458
(grunts)

47:55.792 --> 47:59.000
ABBY (recorded):
Hi. It's me.

48:00.542 --> 48:03.417
Come home.

48:04.834 --> 48:07.166
(chuckles):
Home?

48:07.250 --> 48:10.125
More like a fucking hotel,
right?

48:10.208 --> 48:13.542
Sweetheart, I don't know
why we're here

48:13.625 --> 48:16.083
and why we can't come home.

48:16.166 --> 48:19.000
I don't even fucking care.

48:19.083 --> 48:21.500
You're my home.

48:21.583 --> 48:23.542
I fucking need you, Ray.

48:23.625 --> 48:26.583
We all do.

48:26.667 --> 48:28.792
We don't even have to talk.

48:28.875 --> 48:30.041
Just please come here.

48:33.208 --> 48:35.166
I love you so much.

48:44.709 --> 48:46.667
(sighs)

48:46.750 --> 48:47.834
ANNOUNCER:
...start the seventh round.

48:47.917 --> 48:49.333
There's been
a lot of action so far.

48:49.417 --> 48:50.250
Al, how do you have it?
(bell dings)

48:50.333 --> 48:52.667
ANNOUNCER 2:
It's a very close fight.

48:52.750 --> 48:53.291
I have it 58-56 for...

48:53.375 --> 48:55.500
My boys!

48:55.583 --> 48:56.834
Hey.

48:56.917 --> 48:59.834
(TV continues playing quietly)

49:03.500 --> 49:05.583
(laughs)

49:07.458 --> 49:10.000
Terry, get us some glasses.

49:10.083 --> 49:11.583
Little early, ain't it?

49:11.667 --> 49:13.792
Don't worry about it.

49:24.500 --> 49:26.417
There you go.

49:26.500 --> 49:27.583
Bunch.

49:32.542 --> 49:34.291
So, Pops,
what are we celebrating?

49:37.291 --> 49:38.750
Life.

49:38.834 --> 49:40.166
(laughs)

49:40.250 --> 49:42.250
L'Chaim.

49:46.375 --> 49:48.291
Sip it, Daryll.

49:48.375 --> 49:50.000
(both laughing)

49:50.083 --> 49:51.291
Sip it my ass, motherfucker.

49:55.125 --> 49:56.709
ANNOUNCER:
I'll tell you what, Al,

49:56.792 --> 49:58.041
it's everything
you could possibly want

49:58.125 --> 49:59.166
in a championship fight.

49:59.250 --> 50:00.458
Here they go at each other...

50:00.542 --> 50:01.959
(exhales)

50:02.041 --> 50:05.250
We still have that cot
Bunchy slept on?

50:05.333 --> 50:07.250
Sure.

50:07.333 --> 50:08.792
Good.

50:08.875 --> 50:09.333
(sniffs)

50:09.417 --> 50:12.250
♪ ♪

50:41.000 --> 50:42.917
Is he dead?

50:43.000 --> 50:45.333
Think he's sleeping.

50:45.417 --> 50:47.291
Don't wake him.

50:51.500 --> 50:54.333
♪ ♪

51:16.000 --> 51:18.083
♪ ♪

51:44.166 --> 51:45.250
♪ ♪

52:16.291 --> 52:17.375
(music fades)

52:21.291 --> 52:22.375
♪ ♪

52:53.333 --> 52:54.417
♪ ♪

53:25.333 --> 53:26.417
♪ ♪
